{"tid":1341503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"立場姐姐：前往驗傷中","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T17:23:59.000Z","uid":273803,"like":112,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"67bd3331d95fdde8990dbcf59f6a4c8780972747","tid":1341503,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"轉至立場姐姐Facebook：<br />\n<br />\n要大家擔心不好意思，現已離開現場。雙手、右肩受輕傷有血，後腦腫起，小小頭暈，由上司陪同前往驗傷中。<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家關注，無論如何，請大家在現場一定要冷靜，請千萬注意安全<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n黑社會、黑警全家死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n十萬人睇住立場姐姐俾人打，你班仆街一定走唔甩"},{"pid":"370fdbc58cfb5155080d4576140c56a97753e2b3","tid":1341503,"uid":3893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8QRbvhCGSXo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8QRbvhCGSXo&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=93a9d783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8QRbvhCGSXo</a>"},{"pid":"6aacdf6c2f90f1f7a264ffd864c8accb5d703c83","tid":1341503,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2482524395150061/UzpfSTEwMDAwMjM4NTUzMDE2ODoyMjk1NDE1NjkzODgxMjU5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmlyc6%2Fvideos%2F2482524395150061%2FUzpfSTEwMDAwMjM4NTUzMDE2ODoyMjk1NDE1NjkzODgxMjU5%2F&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=47582efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/mlyc6/videos/2482524395150061/UzpfSTEwMDAwMjM4NTUzMDE2ODoyMjk1NDE1NjkzODgxMjU5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ab7798d88f7401073c724369abff8f51f7140f","tid":1341503,"uid":133533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T